doc.previous: Coffee bars are a representative icon of Pristina[52][65] and they can be found almost everywhere and are also centers of different festivals and events. In the region of Pristina there is Gracanica monastery, which is in the list of UNESCO World Heritage Sites.[66]
after: The Newborn monument was unveiled on 17 February 2008, the day that Kosovo declared its independence. It is decorated with the flags of the 99 nations which recognised its declaration.
The Grand Hotel Prishtina was the property of the Yugoslav government before the Kosovo War in 1999.
